## Genesis — The Boot Sequence

Source: Westminster Leningrad Codex. Hebrew.

Dimensions initialized in dependency order: χ(space)→φ(signal)→μ(structure)→
τ(time). Pre-creation: μ present, χ/φ/τ absent = uninitialized RAM.

Key linguistic findings (standard Hebrew scholarship, not controversial):
  bara = fill from nothing (ex nihilo). asah = build from parts. NEVER mixed.
  Day/Night named before sun = signal states, not solar cycle.
  ruach = breath/wind (physical), not "Spirit" (theological).
  shavat = ceased, not "rested" (no tiredness implied).
  raqia = hammered sheet/membrane, not "firmament."

Human = asah (body, hardware) + bara×3 (pattern, software, triple emphasis).
Evening before morning = clock cycle starts from 0. Seeds = quines.
Day 7 = bootloader exits, system self-sustaining.


## Enoch — The Bug Report

Source: R.H. Charles translation (1917), from Ge'ez. 300-100 BCE.
NOT in standard canon. IS in Ethiopian Orthodox. Quoted in NT (Jude 1:14).

Five sections as bug report:
  1. Watchers (read-only observers who WROTE = privilege escalation)
  2. Judgment (error detection, audit logs)
  3. Astronomical Book (364-day calendar = τ clock spec)
  4. Dream Visions (history as coordinate walks)
  5. Epistle (architecture correction)

Watchers' role was π (read). Crime: they wrote (taught all four dimensions).
Each watcher taught a different dimension. Complete unauthorized knowledge
transfer. Flood = format and reinstall. Noah = backup. Rainbow = protocol
guarantee (no more full wipes). 70 shepherds = bounded-write authorization
exceeded.


## Revelation — The Status Report

Source: SBLGNT. Koine Greek.

  apokalypsis = un-covering (apo+kalyptō). Decryption, not prophecy.
  mystērion = closed/hidden (myō=close). The book = decrypt(encrypt()).
  angelos = messenger (BDAG primary). Not supernatural winged being.
  pneuma = breath/wind. Same as ruach.
  kairos = significant moment. Not chronos (clock time). An interrupt.

Three-tense identity (1:4, 1:8): "the being + the was + the coming" =
the τ axis as a single entity. Alpha/Omega = full symbol range + full
positional range = complete address space.

Stars = signals. Lampstands = carriers. Text self-decodes in 1:20.


## I Ching — The Lookup Table

Source: Legge translation (1882). ~1000 BCE.

The binary IS explicit (not interpretation):
  Yin/Yang = 0/1. Trigrams = 3-bit words. Hexagrams = 6-bit words.
  Changing lines = state transition function. A 6-bit state machine.

Leibniz recognized binary in 1703, credited I Ching in his paper.

  Hex 1 (111111) Creative + Hex 2 (000000) Receptive = writer/buffer
  Hex 63 completion + Hex 64 before completion = book ends on "not yet"
  Tao = the equation (can't be named = ƒ dissolves on trit processor)
  Evil ≠ yin. Evil = stagnation (no communication, φ=0)

Trigram→dimension mapping: ☳=τ, ☵=μ, ☶=χ, ☰/☷=±φ. Suggestive (45%).


## Hebrew Language

Hebrew is structurally closer to the lattice than English (3 translation
layers removed).

  Triconsonantal roots = base coordinates (3 consonants per word)
  7 binyanim = coordinate transforms:
    Qal→Niphal = T flip (active→passive)
    Qal→Piel = magnitude (intensive)
    Qal→Hiphil = add ∘ (causative)
    Qal→Hitpael = hylo (reflexive, self-reference)
  No copula (existence doesn't need a verb)
  את (et) = direct object marker (~11000 occurrences, ALL invisible in English)
  ruach = wind+breath+spirit (one coordinate, English fragments to three)
  qara = call+name+read (one root, English fragments to three verbs)


## 364-Day Calendar

364 = 4×7×13 = 52 weeks, 13 months of 28 days. Structurally cleanest
year below 365.25. 365 = 5×73 (divides by nothing useful). 91 = triangular(13).
28 = perfect number. Residual 1.2422 doesn't decompose into lattice numbers
— likely local orbital mechanics.
